cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.DS 

The paper deals with a networked control architecture, which involves communication and control of a system. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also involves compressed sensing techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves the use of numerical methods and optimization, which could place it in cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) or cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
